{"tid":1627694,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［發夢必食］要好好懲罰呢間鋪","createTime":"2019-10-05T17:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T15:36:02.000Z","uid":331017,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d59230f2d2e7390191c640b150592e527da0ea51","tid":1627694,"uid":331017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:13:36.000Z","msg":"話說，啱啱經過cwb，見肚餓打算去食少少野，成街都冇咩點開，諗住見到邊間就食邊間。點知得呢間開，但一望入去見到啲店員都唔多對路，全部50歲up，個樣係典型廢老藍絲樣。但無計，鬼叫我肚餓咩。<br />\n入到去之後，啲伙記竟然夠膽死同啲食客講緊急法，咁我就聽落去啦，本來打算佢地夠膽講啲廢老言論，即刻頭也不點就走。<br />\n<br />\n我一入去聽到佢地講：<br />\n伙記：依加啲後生仔唔會怕啲差佬㗎啦<br />\n食客：條緊急法過咗之後啲後生就更加唔怕啲差佬，不過你地應該冇咩受影響啦<br />\n伙記：咩冇影響啊，我地啲生意不知淡咗幾多，不過香港都冇咩人鐘意啲大陸人啦，咁鐘意大陸咁辛苦落嚟香港把鬼咩<br />\n伙記：依加香港啲核心價值冇鬼曬，冇曬民主自由，根本大陸就想將佢大陸嗰套塞落嚟香港用，但我地點會肯俾大陸咁做。其實冇人對中国有意見，只係對共產黨有意見。<br />\n<br />\n之後伙記就俾咗個鬼佬點咗過去叫野食，伙記用一口半流利嘅英文落單。而我就特登開個p牌仔Ac上嚟懲罰下呢間鋪頭。希望大家夢遊去開cwb，順便幫下佢地，好好懲罰下呢啲鋪頭，而且食完蛇飲完湯咁補，打狗都打多幾隻。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，黃店一定要好好懲罰！全民補身！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v242cTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv242cTU.jpg&h=4fb7b942&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRBLU7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRBLU7f.jpg&h=48eb8fbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cb050f73cafecbac5e47947ae4bd127fe7a8159","tid":1627694,"uid":202889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:15:10.000Z","msg":"推 食蛇補身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f300f3ffe952c2cbab76e1bbd874141b13feb01","tid":1627694,"uid":5378,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:15:32.000Z","msg":"新account一開即推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打手味濃"},{"pid":"01737b990a2ba76071ab1a29aeef30f7a05ea350","tid":1627694,"uid":124,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"罷賣就夠 藍絲周街都係"},{"pid":"ec8fd365a8adb154054d9a659ba6e59c4061afcc","tid":1627694,"uid":2533,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:19:15.000Z","msg":"呢間bob叔都有幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推介燒味潤腸同靚湯"},{"pid":"22514a2bb939587f214f1bd6a08f7510767547c3","tid":1627694,"uid":10973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f300f3ffe952c2cbab76e1bbd874141b13feb01","tid":1627694,"uid":5378,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:15:32.000Z","msg":"新account一開即推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打手味濃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:23:51.000Z","msg":"本來就係黃店，好多都有介紹"},{"pid":"c3587c5869fad7c546ec4e6bffdc6600be579364","tid":1627694,"uid":351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:26:29.000Z","msg":"放飯唔就腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盡量收工去食"},{"pid":"794e4264eedba7fe0c9a5a7df8c0ac4b533bbc1e","tid":1627694,"uid":226974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a205db9174b8c8d21f375995b5acf5e72dc5dc3","tid":1627694,"uid":106478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:34:28.000Z","msg":"懲罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd31e02ec39b13684997ab119f4b578757e1810","tid":1627694,"uid":279052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:35:29.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係黄，之前食過一次，重幾好食添"},{"pid":"9137963ece9e8808497e44e1df110ac7a6dc2f9c","tid":1627694,"uid":13099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:25:51.000Z","msg":"上次食過，人真係無乜可能真係太近夢遊地點，但啲野幾好食而且伙記都幾好人！<br />\n但之前去唔知佢地係黃，去食多幾次等佢地做到停唔到手，懲罰下啲50後黃絲先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推俾多啲手足補身，場仗先有氣有力打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2805437b5c831b182bded72a9dd2417f045206b9","tid":1627694,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:52:20.000Z","msg":"遊行之前食個蛇膽壯膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89df4dfbcccdeabc8e024b19fd9e809d45644232","tid":1627694,"uid":97120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:53:43.000Z","msg":"朋友開左個良心美食地圖ig想日post夜post黃店既野食吸引更多人幫襯<br />\n將黃店帶入生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/goodwest_standwithhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgoodwest_standwithhk&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=a80c0f87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/goodwest_standwithhk</a><br />\n<br />\n暫時仲好需要大家報料各區既美食<br />\n麻煩影d美食相 同埋打少少食評 最好加埋佢點解係良心餐廳(e.g. 有罷市)<br />\n我地會將佢地po上ig等大家可以一齊去食到佢地提早收鋪！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n投稿熱線：TG @goodwest_standwithhk"},{"pid":"e170fda35e7338746f9c92cfc7245b03d57936c2","tid":1627694,"uid":109671,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"E間食咗好多年。佢地好憎大陸人。對D大陸客好惡。 見過D大陸人三條友只叫一個蛇羹share.."},{"pid":"d1d52686afac061447ce9e70a02c45e0562ce20f","tid":1627694,"uid":314132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要食食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63907748bbfc744c191654f193dca6f03c7de59d","tid":1627694,"uid":13099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f300f3ffe952c2cbab76e1bbd874141b13feb01","tid":1627694,"uid":5378,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:15:32.000Z","msg":"新account一開即推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打手味濃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T05:28:11.000Z","msg":"下面有其他手足都有話係wo"},{"pid":"840b80def171f0a9890b3b42150f24a192752710","tid":1627694,"uid":25028,"like":0,"d